Author: coloraturing
Text: Thank you friend. I’m probably gonna go to urgent care. I’m not used to going to the doc unless I’ve dislocated something or am unconscious but my head hurts pretty bad so you’re right it could be a mild concussion

Author: laisserai
Text: > I'm too fat to be fainting.  Wrong. I fainted more when I was overweight than I do now.   Check your electrolytes. Also go to a doctor about your head. You might have a mild concussion!   You're not a fake. Take care of yourself <3
